INSERT INTO `ri_catalogsearch_fulltext` VALUES ('388', '9', '1', 'KRUKS150|None|KAROLINA RIJEČKA – uokvireni keramički suvenir 17x19 cm|Suvenir Karolina Riječka sastoji se od keramičkog medaljona sa licem riječke heroine Karoline Bellinich, koja je prema predaji spasila grad Rijeku od bombardiranja francuske flote usidrene u Riječkoj luci. Lik Karoline izrađen je prema likovnom predlošku njezinog uljanog portreta koji se čuva u Pomorskom i povijesnom muzeju Hrvatskog primorja u Rijeci. Medaljon se nalazi na smeđoj podlozi a uokviren je zlatnim drvenim okvirom. Medaljon je modeliran te paljen dva puta na 1000 °C, a ukrašen je pravom pozlatom paljenom na temp. od 680°C. Izrada suvenira ostvarena je kao zajednička zamisao za potrebe kazališne predstave „Karolina Riječka“ Hrvatskog narodnog kazališta Ivana pl. Zajca, a uz pomoć Pomorskog i povijesnog muzeja Hrvatskog primorja u Rijeci.|Suvenir Karolina Riječka sastoji se od keramičkog medaljona sa licem riječke heroine Karoline Bellinich, koja je prema predaji spasila grad Rijeku od bombardiranja francuske flote usidrene u Riječkoj luci.|150|1');
INSERT INTO `ri_catalogsearch_fulltext` VALUES ('389', '9', '2', 'KRUKS150|None|CAROLINE OF RIJEKA —framed ceramic souvenir 17x19 cm|CAROLINE OF RIJEKA —framed ceramic souvenir 17x19 cm Click to enlarge The Caroline of Rijeka souvenir is made of a ceramic locket with the face of Rijeka heroin Karolina Bellinich, who, according to legend, saved the city of Rijeka from bombardment by the French Fleet anchored in the port of Rijeka. The figure of Karolina has been created according to an artistic copy of her portrait in oils which is preserved in the Rijeka Maritime and Historical Museum of the Croatian Littoral. The locket is on a beige base and is framed with golden wooden frame. The locket was modelled and fired twice at 1000 °C, and is decorated with real gilding fired at a temperature of 680°C. The souvenir construction is achieved as common idea for needs of the theatre show “Karolina Riječka” performed by the “Ivan pl. Zajc” Croatian National Theatre and with the help of Rijeka Maritime and Historical Museum of the Croatian Littoral.|The Caroline of Rijeka souvenir is made of a ceramic locket with the face of Rijeka heroin Karolina Bellinich, who, according to legend, saved the city of Rijeka from bombardment by the French Fleet anchored in the port of Rijeka.|150|1');
